{"type": "article", "id": 7139, "title": "Cardboard Standing Desks 桌子", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-06T07:23:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234404OKj1MDV3WqtAHs5b.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">随着人们对健康需求的旺盛增长，站立式工作桌正在变得越来越流行。今日，Refold 公司推出的这款桌子引起了人们的关注。这款桌子采用硬纸卡做成，展开的时候是一个站立式的工作台，而折叠起来后像一个大大的手提袋。桌子重量只有13斤，所以你可以方便的带着它移动。而桌子虽然自身重量小，却可以成熟一个正常成年男子的重量。若你觉得站着累了，换一种安装方式，他就可以变低，拉一张椅子，你就可以坐着工作啦。目前他们这个项目在 Kickstarter 上众筹，感兴趣的话你可以点</span><a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1896946361/refold-portable-cardboard-standing-desk?ref=nav_search\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"white-space:normal;\">这里进来</a><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">看看。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234400k6imQ5L8Rs4tubo2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234401p2zB1yAxgv5JmRG7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234401RxXEKPJnh2zLcdw4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052344020OUByYVdJRifbEXo.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234402dY3MQbJChSzcTZ4V.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.703333